    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Driver Side Window</title>
        <para>The school bus driver window is an aluminum two piece sliding window. The window panels, both front and
            rear, are designed to slide forward and aft. The window is equipped with a positive latching device to
            secure the window in a closed locked position.
        </para>
